304
00:15:57.140 --> 00:15:58.580
It's the rock that goes with it.

305
00:15:58.580 --> 00:16:01.220
It's everything else that makes up the ore

306
00:16:01.220 --> 00:16:03.140
that is initially mined.

307
00:16:03.140 --> 00:16:07.540
Before being refined, it's just copper led.

308
00:16:07.540 --> 00:16:11.220
And then after they put the copper or this lead,

309
00:16:11.220 --> 00:16:12.820
this ore into the furnace,

310
00:16:12.820 --> 00:16:17.820
and it kind of slowly, it's called electrolytic refining

311
00:16:18.300 --> 00:16:21.560
